cat << EOF
Althea is intended to be a "stable, easy to use, GUI, IMAP (Internet 
Message Access Protocol) e-mail client for X Windows."  The design 
goal was a stable e-mail client with the richness of usability of 
Microsoft's Outlook, Qualcomm's Eudora, and Cyrusoft's Mulberry.
